Aker Drilling ( OSE : AKD ) is a Norwegian drilling rig operation company . The company will take delivery of two brand new drilling rigs in 2008 with options of further two . The company is part of the Aker Group ( 30,84 % ownership ) and is listed on Oslo Stock Exchange . The company has its headquarters in Stavanger , Norway . The two rigs , with options for two , are ordered from the sister company Aker Kv√¶rner and are of the model Aker H - 6e . The rigs will be semi - submersible . There was previously in the 1970s a different company called Aker Drilling , also that one being part of the Aker Group . That company is now part of Fred . 